						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Stone built into the northern prākāra (inside) of the Vīranārāyaṇasvāmi temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>Sōmēśvara IV—A.D. 1185.</p>						

						<p>This inscription is dated in the <hi rend="bold">4th year</hi> of the reign to <hi rend="bold">Vīra-Sōmēśvaradēva, Vis11vāvasu, Uttarāyaṇa-saṁkrānti,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1185, December 25, Wednesday</hi> (not verifiable).</p>						

						<p>It registers a grant of money made by <hi rend="bold">Vishṇuvardhana Bīchiseṭṭi</hi> to a god</p>						

						</summary>
